flowchart LR
    A[Propose metric and decision purpose] --> B[Define construct, population, and formula]
    B --> C[Implement lineage and quality controls]
    C --> D[Validate reliability, validity, privacy, and interpretation]
    D --> E[Run in shadow mode]
    E --> F{Approve use?}
    F -->|No| B
    F -->|Yes| G[Publish governed metric]
    G --> H[Monitor quality, drift, gaming, and use]
    H --> I{Change required?}
    I -->|Revise| J[Create new version]
    J --> C
    I -->|Deprecate| K[Deprecate with successor and migration]
    K --> L[Retire while preserving history]
    I -->|No| M[Scheduled review]
    M --> H

    Q[Owner, steward, governance, and decision record] -. applies throughout .-> A
    Q -. applies throughout .-> D
    Q -. applies throughout .-> G
    Q -. applies throughout .-> L
